<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Increased Subscription Error Rates>
We are investigating increased AWS Marketplace subscription error rates.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Service is operating normally: [RESOLVED] Increased Subscription Error Rates>
Between 1:36 AM and 4:07 AM PST we experienced increased AWS Marketplace subscription error rates. The issue has been resolved and the service is operating normally.
